{"tid":1035441,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★假如中大蝗蟲團遇上辮子姑娘，會點？","createTime":"2019-02-24T15:17:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-24T15:37:27.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ec3415b09c0dba6c3d46808d32f5254a6062b6a7","tid":1035441,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T15:17:57.000Z","msg":"車軌亡魂 化身辮子女鬼<br />\n<br />\n究竟辮子姑娘是何方神聖？何故會在中大校園出沒？<br />\n<br />\n有傳那位姑娘原為一名束幵辮子的中大女生，因不堪被男友拋棄，於校園內上吊自縊，自此，事發地點附近開始傳出有束辮女鬼出沒，專嚇男生！<br />\n<br />\n另一版本則和內地偷渡客有關：話說六、七十年代，不少內地人偷渡來港，部分人匿藏於往來廣州與九龍的火車上，待到叅後便跳車逃走，一位內地姑娘有樣學樣，於某月某夜在馬料水跳車，殊不知在跳車一刻，她頭上的辮子被車廂的隙縫卡住，可憐那位姑娘的辮子、頭皮、臉皮被一併扯掉，當場慘死。<br />\n<br />\n由於死得冤枉，有傳那位辮子姑娘的魂魄一直徘徊在中大校園，陰魂不散&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://the-sun.on.cc/channels/adult/20051102/20051101225915_0000.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthe-sun.on.cc%2Fchannels%2Fadult%2F20051102%2F20051101225915_0000.html&d=NJeO18TDpfQgexRQIuB%2FGIdddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=6c74eeab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://the-sun.on.cc/channels/adult/20051102/20051101225915_0000.html</a>"},{"pid":"ee58ddd6e5f03467b74d06fceef2bcac437d110c","tid":1035441,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T15:18:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57d8fa3ee4f78f3728f4345466a18bd606e7b09f","tid":1035441,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T15:20:30.000Z","msg":"老子甚麼鬼都不信！"},{"pid":"e6d2eceadc77c04fe2aa612dcb2ca3b25d8b882c","tid":1035441,"uid":90,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T15:22:31.000Z","msg":"Why so late still 9up?<br />\nNo need work today?"},{"pid":"6cefd9ad6e6867be1276ca988e4bd7d67d4ee59e","tid":1035441,"uid":19454,"like":0,